title: Wahoo's - Campus Pointe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg

The menu includes different filling choices for tacos, burritos, enchiladas, and bowls. Veg filling include marinated tofu, saute mixed vegetable teriyaki, or vegetarian rice and bean(has cheese).
